User uploads image → S3 bucket
        ↓
Analyzer Lambda (triggered on upload)
        ↓
   ┌────────────┬─────────────────┬──────────┐
Rekognition   Bedrock Nova Lite   Polly
(moderation   (generates caption) (text-to-
+ labels)                          speech)
   └────────────┴─────────────────┴──────────┘
        ↓
   DynamoDB (stores results)
        ↓
   API Gateway + Lambda (serves results via REST)
        ↓
   S3 static frontend (displays results to user)
